These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, skydiving, dancing, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, snowboarding, volleyball, skateboarding
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | collecting | dancing | skydiving  |
| Sport   | water-polo | volleyball   | skateboarding  | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, asparagus, plum, garlic
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, electrician, videographer, security-guard
1. the security-guard is not to the left of the security-guard##8
2. the person eating kale is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5
3. the person eating kale is the electrician##1
4. the person eating garlic is between the person eating kale and the person eating asparagus##2
5. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating plum and the entrepreneur##7
6. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
7. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the entrepreneur##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | plum | asparagus          | garlic | kale     |
| Job    | videographer      | security-guard | entrepreneur | electrician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, police-officer, firefighter, dancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, sports, crime, western
1. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the firefighter##8
2. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the police-officer is in an even position##4
5. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
7. the dancer is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | firefighter     | dancer |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | western   | animation | crime    |

