.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, r&b, soul, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, badminton, skiing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of electronic is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the fan of classical is the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | r&b         | electronic   | classical    |
| Sport         | rugby | skiing | badminton | golf |

