.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, time-travel, documentary, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, swimming, water-polo, cricket
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7
2. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching sports movies##7
4. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
5. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's sport is swimming##7
6. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
7. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | documentary | martial-arts | sports    |
| Sport         | golf | cricket   | water-polo   | swimming |

