2. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
5. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
6. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
7. the person eating watermelon is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | watermelon | apple | radish  | banana |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | punk         | metal | house |

