.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, coffee, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, basketball, cycling, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's sport is cycling##7
3. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
6. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | 7up      | coffee | milk | iced-tea   |
| Sport      | sailing | cycling | weightlifting  | basketball |

