3. the pilot is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the pilot##7
5. the paramedic is not to the right of the mechanic##8
6. the mechanic is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the paramedic##7

