.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, blues, punk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, train, subway, van
1. the fan of salsa is between the fan of punk and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
5. the person driving the train is the person driving the train##1
6. the fan of blues is not the person driving the subway##6
7. the fan of punk is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
8. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | salsa | blues | d&b |
| Transport     | van | train       | bike  | subway    |

