.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, cucumber, potato, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, baking, photography, woodworking
1. the person eating potato is not to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person eating cucumber##8
3. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating potato is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
7. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | cucumber        | watermelon | potato      | apricot    |
| Hobby   | gardening | photography   | baking | woodworking |

