3. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
4. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is reading##2

