.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, banana, peas, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy, satire, animation
 1. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 2. the person eating corn is not to the left of the person eating peas##8
 3. the person eating lime is the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person watching satire movies##8
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the person eating lime##8
10. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person watching drama movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | banana    | peas | lime | corn |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | animation  | satire     | fantasy    |

