.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog, goat, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, airplane, tram, scooter
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person driving the tram##6
2. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
3. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
6. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
7. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | goldfish  | guinea-pig | dog  | goat  |
| Transport   | boat | airplane   | scooter | tram |

