.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, turtle, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, bus, helicopter
1. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the rat##6
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
4. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the snowmobile##7
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the helicopter and the owner of the turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig    | goldfish | rat | turtle |
| Transport   | tram | helicopter      | bus     | snowmobile     |

 